<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<title>商品列表</title>
</head>
{literal}
<style type="text/css">
#table {
	width: 100%;
	border: 1px solid #EEE;
	font-size: 14px;
}

#table th {
	background: #ffffff;
	border-bottom: 1px solid #CCC;
	padding: 4px;
	text-align: center;
}

#table td {
	border: 1px solid #EEE;
	padding: 4px;
	text-align: left;
}

a {
	color: #000000;
	text-decoration: none;
}
</style>
{/literal} 
<body>
<table id="table">
	<tr>
		<th>使用指南</th>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td><a href="#">1.查看商品,请先选择分类,在某类别下查找具体商品,输入商品名称(可以不是全称),进行查找</a></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td><a href="#">2.添加商品时,必须输入商品名称与警告库存,同时不能添加样式</a></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td><a href="#">3.编辑商品时,可以添加样式</a></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td><a href="#">4.添加样式时,举例:手机的颜色是红色,此价格是500.00,不能再添加此手机是红色的样式</a></td>
	</tr>
</table>
</body>
{literal}
<script type="text/javascript">
	var obj = document.getElementById("table");
	for ( var i = 0; i < obj.rows.length; i++) {
		obj.rows[i].onmouseover = function() {
			this.style.background = "#bbdde5";
		}
		obj.rows[i].onmouseout = function() {
			this.style.background = "";
		}
	}
</script>
{/literal}
</html>